Revision history for even-codex

0.05 2026-05-31
    - add Even Hub listing metadata, greyscale icon and background assets,
      and governed submission content for `D2-Codex`
    - add a simulator-backed screenshot capture workflow for Hub submission
    - prove the richer manifest fields still pack into a valid `.ehpk`

0.04 2026-05-31
    - upgrade the `D2-Codex` Even Hub app from a packaging-valid starter into
      a user-friendly phone-side setup and status workflow
    - rebuild the glasses view into three readable containers with header
      refresh, detail cycling, and clearer exit guidance
    - document and verify the stronger Even plugin UX through governed Docker
      tests and release records

0.03 2026-05-31
    - add a real Even Hub `D2-Codex` package manifest with documented
      edition, version floor, entrypoint, and network permission structure
    - add a Vite and TypeScript based Even Hub SDK app that creates the
      startup glasses page, persists the bridge origin, and handles root
      double-click exit plus foreground lifecycle events
    - add reproducible `build:hub` and `pack:hub` workflows so the skill can
      build `dist/index.html` and package `dist/d2-codex.ehpk`

0.02 2026-05-31
    - add a runnable LAN bridge slice with workspace-to-Codex pairing through
      `dashboard even-codex.start add <codex-session-id>`
    - add `dashboard even-codex.start` to serve the Even connector on port
      `6789` by default with `/health`, `/bootstrap`, and `/plugin/`
    - bundle the first Even plugin web app inside the skill repo and verify it
      with Docker tests and Playwright

0.01 2026-05-31
    - bootstrap governed even-codex skill repository
    - add production software specification in SPEC.md
    - add minimal spec metadata module and Docker-verified tests
    - add explicit local-network deployment mode to the production specification
    - map the specification into phased SOW workstreams
    - add Even::Codex::Protocol as the first runtime contract module
